songs.lyrics:
[Refrain]
Hexagons, hexagons, hexagons

[Verse]
I'm  so emotional
But  I can't help it
My heart says move on
My mind is, is left behind
I'm  feeling so out of it
The  stars running through my heart
The density is down on me
But  then I look at the stars again
And I remember that I'm a part of it
I like to drink Chlorophyll
And eat like particles
I'm  feeling like Merkabah
Hexagons ones are my favorite ones
Even the pentagons, oh
I love the octagons, oh

[Refrain]
Hexagons, hexagons, hexagons
Hexagons, hexagons, hexagons
songs.title: Hexagons
